<doc id="41702" wikidata="Q16874989" url="?curid=41702" title="Signal compression">
<text>Signal compression is the use of various techniques to increase the quality or quantity of signal parameters transmitted through a given telecommunications channel.

Types of signal compression include:

*Bandwidth compression
*Data compression
*Dynamic range compression
*Gain compression
*Image compression
*Lossy compression
*One-way compression function</text><links>
